    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >捣蛋幽灵：附身大作战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >捣蛋幽灵：附身大作战 - 附身物品、大搞破坏、并在混战中存活到最后！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043520/extras/4b83c16513ee1a487862234c4a270854.poster.avif?t=1767708945\" width=600 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043520/extras/4b83c16513ee1a487862234c4a270854.webm?t=1767708945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043520/extras/4b83c16513ee1a487862234c4a270854.mp4?t=1767708945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >屋中的物品多么死气沉沉，是时候用你强大的附身能力让它们活跃起来了！利用物品战斗、逃跑，或是在周遭一片混乱时摆出帅气的姿态！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043520/extras/e8a632176433991951c3b42262c3f796.poster.avif?t=1767708945\" width=600 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043520/extras/e8a632176433991951c3b42262c3f796.webm?t=1767708945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043520/extras/e8a632176433991951c3b42262c3f796.mp4?t=1767708945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一场令人胆战心惊的狂欢盛宴！恐怖的怪物来袭，如果调皮捣蛋的幽灵们被它追上，就要魂飞魄散啦！手忙脚乱？是的！勾心斗角？当然！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043520/extras/669a8aca2e90056407c41691b873540f.poster.avif?t=1767708945\" width=600 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043520/extras/669a8aca2e90056407c41691b873540f.webm?t=1767708945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043520/extras/669a8aca2e90056407c41691b873540f.mp4?t=1767708945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽情破坏，将善念抛之脑后，这就是你的取胜技巧！怪物固然可怕，但稍加利用便是移动的死亡机器！用看似无害的能力让你的对手陷入困境吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043520/extras/87adf454c11b4e0670bc645f6c7b057a.poster.avif?t=1767708945\" width=600 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043520/extras/87adf454c11b4e0670bc645f6c7b057a.webm?t=1767708945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043520/extras/87adf454c11b4e0670bc645f6c7b057a.mp4?t=1767708945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关卡中散布着大量的道具和陷阱，为你的捣蛋行径助一臂之力……问题是，如果怪物已经扼住你小小的咽喉，你还能施展浑身解数逃离吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;那么……现在究竟有什么游戏内容？！&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >问得太好了！在游戏发售首日，你就能玩到以下精彩内容：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8个独特的关卡，其中的陷阱都基于现实物理原理打造，还有各种玩具！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20件可收集的附身服饰，探索和升级之路绝不枯燥！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每日和每周挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每周排行榜！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幽灵之路，前进就有新精彩！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大量奖励，包括头像、表情、特效、个性化领奖台……等你来拿！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏最多可支持4名玩家坐在沙发上分屏进行本地游戏。或者，大家也可以一起联机，在线开启派对盛宴！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你还拥有名为“幽灵小屋”的专属空间……用收集到的糖果为它添置新的装饰吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
